WEBVTT

00:00.559 --> 00:02.517
On the banks of the Brisbane River...

00:02.679 --> 00:04.803
...lies this city with a fantastic climate.

00:05.695 --> 00:09.875
Brisbane is a popular tourist destination, lively and dynamic...

00:10.201 --> 00:13.049
...that's bathed in beautiful sunshine all year round.

00:13.767 --> 00:16.180
It's the third largest city in Australia...

00:16.631 --> 00:18.752
...with a population of two million people.

00:19.415 --> 00:23.032
The best things to do in Brisbane are outdoor activities...

00:23.219 --> 00:25.805
...such as cycling, climbing or hiking.

00:26.827 --> 00:30.020
This is a fun and friendly city with a vibrant music scene,...

00:30.349 --> 00:34.143
...venues, restaurants and all kinds of bars to choose from.

